21\u002F09\u002F11\u002Fjs-to-python-10-container-types-part-2\u002F","Learning Python From a JavaScript Angle (10): Container Types, Part 2","2021-09-11 00:00:10",{"url":1093,"title":1094,"date":1095},"\u002Fen\u002Fpython\u002F2021\u002F09\u002F09\u002Fjs-to-python-08-bmi-calculator-1\u002F","Learning Python From a JavaScript Angle (8) - BMI Calculator (1)","2021-09-09 00:00:10",[1097,1102,1107],{"url":1098,"title":1099,"date":1100,"readingMinutes":1101},"\u002Fen\u002Fpython\u002F2021\u002F10\u002F02\u002Flearn-python-from-javascript-31-finale\u002F","Learning Python from a JavaScript Angle (31): So What Do You Want to Learn Next?","2021-10-02 00:00:05","4",{"url":1103,"title":1104,"date":1105,"readingMinutes":1106},"\u002Fen\u002Fpython\u002F2021\u002F10\u002F01\u002Flearning-python-from-javascript-30-web-scraping\u002F","Learning Python From JavaScript (30): Building a Web Scraper","2021-10-01 00:00:10","6",{"url":1108,"title":1109,"date":1110,"readingMinutes":1106},"\u002Fen\u002Fpython\u002F2021\u002F09\u002F30\u002Fpython-29-beautifulsoup\u002F","Learning Python From a JavaScript Angle (29) - BeautifulSoup","2021-09-30 00:00:10",1784087340805]